name: ch-api-client-swift
description: Openapi generated swift client for CloudHospital

scripts.build: openapi-generator-cli version-manager set 5.0.0-beta3 && openapi-generator-cli generate -g swift5 --additional-properties=projectName=CloudHospitalClient,swiftUseApiNamespace=true,podVersion=1.3.9 -o . -i https://api-int.icloudhospital.com/swagger/v1/swagger.json
scripts.build-alamofire: openapi-generator-cli version-manager set 5.0.0-beta3 && openapi-generator-cli generate -g swift5 --additional-properties=projectName=CloudHospitalClient,podVersion=1.3.9,responseAs=Combine --library alamofire -o . -i https://api-int.icloudhospital.com/swagger/v1/swagger.json

author: hyounoosung@gmail.com
